OL,4,Cto stop triple killer speaks out
OL,6,FThe NHS worker says she was silenced
OL,7,Fwhen she tried to blow the whistle
OL,8,Fover safety concerns at the trust -
OL,9,Fthe stress even led her to contemplate
OL,10,Fsuicide.
OL,12,FIt comes as an independent report
OL,13,Frevealed a series of failures by
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust during the care and
OL,16,Ftreatment of Calocane, before he
OL,17,Fkilled three people.
