OL,6,FCalocane, who was diagnosed with
OL,7,Fparanoid schizophrenia, killed Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and Ian
OL,9,FCoates in Nottingham in June 2023.
OL,11,FThe victims' families are calling for
OL,12,Fa full statutory inquiry to examine
OL,13,Ftheir deaths and "wider failings" in
OL,14,Fmental health services.
OL,16,FThe independent review found:
