OL,3,CStaff member at NHS trust that failed
OL,4,Cto stop triple killer speaks out
OL,6,FITV News has spoken to a staff member
OL,7,Fwho worked at Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FHealthcare NHS foundation Trust during
OL,9,FCalocane's treatment, though she
OL,10,Fwasn't involved in his care.
OL,12,FThe mental health worker, who has
OL,13,Fasked to remain anonymous, claims when
OL,14,Fshe tried to raise other safety
OL,15,Fconcerns at the trust she was targeted
OL,16,Fby her bosses.
OL,18,F"I was ostracised and victimised by
OL,19,Fthe organisation and I felt
OL,20,Fpowerless", she told ITV News.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@JO]
