OL,3,CStaff member at NHS trust that failed
OL,4,Cto stop triple killer speaks out
OL,6,F"I felt pushed to the brink - and even
OL,7,Fconsidered taking my own life."
OL,9,FShe echoes the report's findings about
OL,10,Fover-stretched staff.
OL,12,F"Cost-cutting is down to the bone. We
OL,13,Fjust couldn't keep staff because of
OL,14,Fthe working conditions.
OL,16,F"People don't go to work to make
OL,17,Fmistakes. It's the system that has
OL,18,Fallowed the failures."
