OL,6,FNHS England bosses admit the "system
OL,7,Fgot it wrong".
OL,9,FEvery mental health trust in England
OL,10,Fhas now been ordered to set out action
OL,11,Fplans for how they treat people who
OL,12,Fhave a serious mental illness.
OL,14,FThey have also been instructed not to
OL,15,Fdischarge people if they do not attend
OL,16,Fappointments.
