OL,6,FIn a statement the victims' families
OL,7,Fsaid: "There are grave questions to be
OL,8,Fanswered about how multiple
OL,9,Forganizations failed to respond to the
OL,10,Frisk he posed; allowing him to roam
OL,11,Fthe streets and kill three innocent
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,F"We are fighting for justice for them,
OL,15,Fbut also for accountability, improved
OL,16,Fmental health care, and improved
OL,17,Fsafety for all in society."
