OL,6,FSecretary of State for Health and
OL,7,FSocial Care, Wes Streeting, said: "It
OL,8,Fis important that the families and the
OL,9,Fpublic have confidence in the system,
OL,10,Fand we have worked closely with NHS
OL,11,FEngland to ensure the publication of
OL,12,Fthis report in full. Sunlight is the
OL,13,Fbest disinfectant.
OL,15,F"The findings will help to support an
OL,16,Finquiry into this attack and we'll set
OL,17,Fout the next steps as this develops".
