OL,6,FIfti Majid, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust has expressed his
OL,9,F"deepest condolences" to the families
OL,10,Fof Calocane's victims.
OL,12,F"We apologise unreservedly for the
OL,13,Fopportunities we missed in the care of
OL,14,FValdo Calocane and accept the Theemis
OL,15,Freport in its entirety including its
OL,16,Ffindings and recommendations.
